{"tid":2034654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共已經走頭無路","createTime":"2020-05-25T11:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T16:10:44.000Z","uid":37038,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"41fc3007d02241bce6605e2c94fe8733fec595ff","tid":2034654,"uid":37038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"中共立港版國安法<br />\n目的唔係針對香港人或維園阿伯最憎既民主黨<br />\n<br />\n中共最驚既永遠唔係香港人<br />\n亦都唔係佢所講既咩外國勢力港獨勢力<br />\n<br />\n佢驚既係佢地自己中共既人<br />\n一班真正影響到中共勢力分怖既人<br />\n一班利用香港散水洗錢既大陸高層幹部<br />\n一班掌握疫情真相既人<br />\n<br />\n中共咁急要硬推國安<br />\n因為佢已經走頭無路<br />\n<br />\n佢愈亂咁黎<br />\n代表佢愈驚<br />\n代表佢愈脆弱<br />\n代表佢已經水深火熱<br />\n<br />\n黎緊半年應該會發生大事"},{"pid":"a50a88a2bb4e54e9a90f502deed9e9f17cc4f645","tid":2034654,"uid":130901,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:05:51.000Z","msg":"走投。。"},{"pid":"a25172bb4cc2df826bcb75d94dc1c0f90997fcb8","tid":2034654,"uid":241530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"我都係咁諗, 覺得多少都關內政事"},{"pid":"794b91eed77879ef7b5afd1c69e2af25e8b74bc4","tid":2034654,"uid":19986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:06:48.000Z","msg":"大事？ 唔好再general啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a59d5ffc7ba3efa68fd52802cd23276badedddf","tid":2034654,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"794b91eed77879ef7b5afd1c69e2af25e8b74bc4","tid":2034654,"uid":19986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:06:48.000Z","msg":"大事？ 唔好再general啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:07:48.000Z","msg":"郭文貴：中共過埋2020年仲未收皮我就跳樓死！<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2661924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2661924&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3i%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=89a8be02\" data-ef-url=\"https:/